  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "🦅 Business Partner & Team Leader-in-Training (Sales)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Highlights:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Build Your Own Business</strong> 💼</li>\n  <li><strong>Transparent Advancement Criteria</strong> 📈</li>\n  <li><strong>Uncapped Earning Potential</strong> 💰</li>\n  <li><strong>Directly Work with MNC Clients</strong> 🌐</li>\n  <li><strong>Full Mentorship &amp; Business Development</strong> 🎓</li>\n  <li><strong>Be Your Own Boss</strong> 👑</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>About the Role:</strong></p>\n<p>Tired of the traditional 9-to-5? 😴 This is not just a job; it's an opportunity to build your own team and run your own business in the dynamic world of sales and marketing. We are looking for ambitious individuals with an entrepreneurial spirit to join us on a structured path to leadership.</p>\n<p>Your journey will be divided into clear phases:</p>\n<ol>\n  <li><strong>Mastering the Foundation:</strong> You will start on the ground, engaging with customers at roadshows, events, and in residential areas. This is where you'll build the core skills in sales and client relations. 🤝</li>\n  <li><strong>Learning to Lead:</strong> As you progress, you will receive extensive training in personal development, coaching, and business management. 🧑‍🏫</li>\n  <li><strong>Building Your Team:</strong> You will mentor and lead your own team of sales and marketing professionals, helping them achieve their goals. 🚀</li>\n  <li><strong>Running Your Enterprise:</strong> With transparent criteria for every step, you will advance into a management role, overseeing operations, managing finances, and driving your own business unit's success. 📈</li>\n</ol>\n<p>This role requires a high level of resilience and a commitment to personal and business growth. We provide the platform, the clients (MNCs), and the mentorship—you provide the drive. 🔥</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Who We're Looking For:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>An Entrepreneurial Mindset:</strong> You are ambitious, driven, and aspire to be your own boss. 💪</li>\n  <li><strong>Resilient &amp; Driven:</strong> You see challenges as opportunities and are motivated by results. 🎯</li>\n  <li><strong>A Strong Communicator:</strong> You enjoy interacting with people and can build trust easily. 🗣️</li>\n  <li><strong>A Leader in the Making:</strong> You have a passion for mentoring others and a desire to build a successful team. 🌟</li>\n  <li><strong>Singaporean/PR Only</strong> 🇸🇬</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Ready to build your own empire? Apply now!</strong> 📩</p>",
